&lt;blockquote&gt;⚠️ &lt;b&gt;Recommend Immediate Vet Visit&lt;/b&gt;

I understand your desire to know exactly what to expect from the scans, especially when you&#x27;re worried about Tank. However, as an AI, I cannot diagnose or predict the specific findings of veterinary diagnostic imaging like X-rays or ultrasound.

Only the emergency veterinarian, after performing a thorough physical exam and interpreting the actual images they take of Tank, will be able to tell you precisely what the scans reveal. They will be looking for signs of a foreign body, the location of any potential obstruction, and assessing the condition of his intestines.

My role is to provide general information and guide you on the best course of action. In this urgent situation, that means getting Tank to the emergency vet as quickly as possible so they can perform these essential diagnostics and make an accurate diagnosis.

Please focus on getting Tank to the clinic immediately.&lt;/blockquote&gt;

⚠️ &lt;i&gt;Please seek immediate vet care first&lt;/i&gt;</blockquote>

